{"tid":1045781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"已經失眠左成兩個幾月 點搞","createTime":"2019-03-03T18:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T04:58:22.000Z","uid":2215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6520ad94e71dc6897cd1711e7eb96d6aa6489777","tid":1045781,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:39:16.000Z","msg":"晚晚想訓都訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f4f86f3e64171997db9d6b9e9460e1611a972f","tid":1045781,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/anthonywongnotsleepfacebook_68957618758d1396ab78d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fanthonywongnotsleepfacebook_68957618758d1396ab78d0.png&h=86c54056&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33f1a24aaedfedea52a6b1be6ca909e10cc20a04","tid":1045781,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f4f86f3e64171997db9d6b9e9460e1611a972f","tid":1045781,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:40:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgs.nmplus.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/anthonywongnotsleepfacebook_68957618758d1396ab78d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.nmplus.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2Fanthonywongnotsleepfacebook_68957618758d1396ab78d0.png&h=86c54056&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:40:42.000Z","msg":"=.=&quot;"},{"pid":"ccde3a7e228a487d55f840f154a4b096d38a7d10","tid":1045781,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T18:56:06.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=k%2BTG7AB%2FuAEPzMnKacyWv0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=25f10fa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"6dba24c55e30f46811a85391a7c42fff94707137","tid":1045781,"uid":2215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T19:01:37.000Z","msg":"好怕第二日來臨既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726631a09f2c57bf2991ccc92c7eb6ad3513079f","tid":1045781,"uid":230659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:29:41.000Z","msg":"關唔關食煙飲茶飲咖啡事<br />\n近日大壓力<br />\n食煙多咗飲咖啡都係<br />\n今日只係食咗一枝<br />\n但飲咗茶<br />\n到宜家個腦都好多野諗<br />\n訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa736b0a753a8399d9a7eef899d357c0c43766fe","tid":1045781,"uid":186292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:36:11.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"8e7d5e69c3a62a4eaac26444db5296512d17ad82","tid":1045781,"uid":230659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T20:48:38.000Z","msg":"天光啦屌。"},{"pid":"a46fcfc6b41652c16e7b96493d402a0c7e00bf3a","tid":1045781,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T21:17:24.000Z","msg":"我瞓"},{"pid":"046495f9719c2933c0a169641cf290c9c6725c8a","tid":1045781,"uid":200699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"睇中醫 你無褪黑素"},{"pid":"35e71e48aa2be411869079c3335fb509f6cb7953","tid":1045781,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score